<table style="width:98%; border-collapse:collapse; margin:0px auto;padding-top:10px;">
    <tr height="60px">
        <td style="font-size:16px; padding-left:30px;">
            {% if certificate_type == 'nagorik' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person is {% if (data.resident|default('permanent')) == 'temporary' %}a temporary resident{% else %}a permanent resident{% endif %} of this Union and is a citizen of Bangladesh. His/Her conduct and character is good.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'trade' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person operates a business in this Union and regularly renews his Trade License.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'warish' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person is the heir of the deceased person and the legal successor of the related property.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'character' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; His/Her conduct and character is good. He/She is not involved in any immoral activities.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'new-voter-' or certificate_type == 'new-voter' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; He/She is {% if (data.resident|default('permanent')) == 'temporary' %}a temporary resident{% else %}a permanent resident{% endif %} of this Union. He/She is a natural-born citizen of Bangladesh and is known to me. He/She could not be included in the voter list as he/she was not present during the preparation and updating of the voter list. I recommend him/her for being a new voter. I wish for his/her overall welfare and progress.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'voter' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; He/She desires to transfer his/her voter status from this Union to another place. Therefore, this certification is being provided for the transfer of his/her voter ID.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'vumihin' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; The above-mentioned person is a landless citizen. A request is being made to the Government for his/her rehabilitation.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'death' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is hereby certified that the above-mentioned person, {{ data.deceased_name }}, died. Date of death: {{ data.death_date | date('d-m-Y') }}. This certification is provided for appropriate use.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'yearlyincome' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the annual income of the above-mentioned person is Taka {{ data.yearly_income | number_format(0, '.', ',') }}.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'disability' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person is disabled and is entitled to disabled person facilities as per government rules.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'student' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person is a bonafide student of our Union area.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'obibahito' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; He/She is {% if (data.resident|default('permanent')) == 'temporary' %}a temporary resident{% else %}a permanent resident{% endif %} of this Union. To the best of my knowledge, he/she has not entered into wedlock to date and his/her conduct and moral character is good and praiseworthy.
                <br><br>
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; I wish for his/her overall welfare and progress.
                <br><br>
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is to be noted that if any information provided in the application form by the applicant or the verifier is found to be incorrect, both parties shall be held personally responsible and this certificate shall be considered void.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'bibahito' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is hereby certified that the above-mentioned person is married and his/her marriage was solemnized on {{ data.marriage_date | date('d-m-Y') }}.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'ekoinam' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is hereby certified that the name of the above-mentioned person has been recorded as the same name across multiple documents.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'punobibaho' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person has not remarried.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'protibondi' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; The above-mentioned person is physically speech and hearing impaired. The kind attention of the concerned authorities is sought for his/her proper rehabilitation.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'onapotti' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is hereby certified that the above-mentioned person is not involved in any kind of objectionable activities. No Objection Certificate is hereby provided to him/her.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'prottyon' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; He/She is {% if (data.resident|default('permanent')) == 'temporary' %}a temporary resident{% else %}a permanent resident{% endif %} of this Union and is personally known to me. To the best of my knowledge, he/she is not involved in any unlawful activities. His/her conduct and character is good. I wish for his/her overall welfare.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'onumoti' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; I hereby grant voluntary permission for participating in the aforementioned purpose. {{ data.permission_reason_bn }}
                <br><br>
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; I wish for his/her overall welfare and progress.
                <br><br>
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is to be noted that if any information provided in the application form by the applicant or the verifier is found to be incorrect, both parties shall be held personally responsible and this certificate shall be considered void.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'rastakhonon' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Permission is hereby granted for road excavation within this Union, subject to completion of the work within the specified timeframe.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'sonaton' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; It is hereby certified that the above-mentioned person is a follower of the Sanatan (Hindu) faith and regularly participates in religious activities.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'nodibanga' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; The above-mentioned person has lost his/her homestead due to river erosion and is currently residing in this area.
            {% elseif certificate_type == 'Onnanno' %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; He/She is {% if (data.resident|default('permanent')) == 'temporary' %}a temporary resident{% else %}a permanent resident{% endif %} of this Union and is personally known to me. To the best of my knowledge, he/she is not involved in any unlawful activities. His/her conduct and character is good. I wish for his/her overall welfare.
                <br>
                This certificate is issued based on the verification of information provided by the Ward Member ({{ approval.verifier_name_bn }}) of this Union. It is to be noted that if any information provided in the application form by the applicant or the verifier is found to be incorrect, both parties shall be held personally responsible and this certificate shall be considered void.
            {% else %}
                &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; This is to certify that the above-mentioned person is known to me.
            {% endif %}
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
